Project Overview
This project analyzes customer churn data to identify high-risk segments and provide actionable, data-driven retention strategies. The analysis focuses on customer behavior patterns using SQL and presents insights through an interactive Excel dashboard.

---

## 📌 Key Insights
- Customers with low engagement (low frequency & recency) show the highest churn rates
- Mid-value customers present the biggest opportunity for retention improvement
- A small segment of high-value customers contributes significantly to overall revenue

